---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../layout/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Introduction">
	<Header title="Loxt" description="Loxt is a simple and lightweight console logger with 0 external dependencies.">
		<div class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2 gap-2 justify-center rounded-lg bg-slate-900 bg-opacity-50">
			<pre>npm install loxt</pre>
			<button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('npm install loxt').then(() => alert('Copied successfully!'))">
				<svg preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1.2em" height="1.2em"
					class="inline-block fill-current text-gray-200 cursor-pointer hover:text-white mb-1" aria-hidden="true">
					<path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
						d="M8 5H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-1M8 5a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2M8 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2m0 0h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3m2 4H10m0 0l3-3m-3 3l3 3">
					</path>
				</svg>
			</button>
		</div>
	</Header>
	<main class="mt-5 gap-5 grid justify-center">
		<div class="border-4 border-blue-700 rounded-md"></div>
		<p>Efficient Logging, loxt works for Node.js, Browser, Deno, and in the future <a class="text-blue-600"
				href="https://bun.sh" target="_blank">bun</a></p>
	</main>

	<style>
		main div {
			width: 483px;
			height: 193px;
			background-size: cover;
			background-position: center;
			background-repeat: no-repeat;
			background-image: url('/example01.png');
		}
	</style>
</Layout>